        <p>
            NSK is a Lim's family business and it starts with a small kiosk selling groceries and household goods at the Chow Kit market in 1985.
            Six years later, at 1991 NSK or better known as the New Seng Kee developed from a small kiosk business to a retail store that sells a variety of grocery and household items,
