        </p>
        <p>
            NSK continues to expand its business by opening NSK Selayang that combines two concepts of retail and wholesale businesses in August 2003. 
            Selayang wholesale market is located near NSK Selayang and it gives an advantage as a strategic business location. 
            On above requirements and market demand, NSK Selayang began operating 24 hours beginning on January 1, 
            2007 and therefore NSK Selayang as a business center in line with the vision of building the company into the largest wholesaler in Malaysia.
        </p>
        <p> 
